{{codepointer|r=Strife|Status change}} '''A_FlameDie'''
(''no parameter'')
Sets the {{Flag|NOGRAVITY}} flag and changes the z velocity to some value 0-3. This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|FlameMissile}} and derived classes.
